.nr nS 0
.Pp
.Sh 
.nr nS 1
.Ft int
.Fn prop_load "void *obj" "int fd"
.Pp
.Ft int
.Fn prop_save "void *obj" "int fd"
.nr nS 0
The
.Fn prop_load
function loads an object's property table from
.Fa fd ,
and
.Fn prop_save
saves an object's property table to
.Fa fd .
